message.content:
I need to identify the deposit into the bank, which would be listed as "Bank Deposits" on the balance sheet.

Looking at the balance sheet provided, I can see:

| Account | Initial_amount | Initial_date | End_amount | End_date |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Bank Deposits | 15000000.00 | 2023-12-31 | -129032.26 | 2024-02-05 |

The task asks me to extract the initial and final value for funds deposited into a bank.

So the initial value of Bank Deposits is 15000000.00 as of 2023-12-31.
The end value of Bank Deposits is -129032.26 as of 2024-02-05.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '15000000.00', 'end value': '-129032.26'}}
```
